DESCRIPTION: High Voltage Fairies in the Pit – Nu & Alt Metal Special Every last Friday of the month the Fairy Pit opens up at Viper Room. This time we’re going old school with a Nu & Alt Metal Special heavy on Linkin Park\, Korn\, Slipknot\, System of a Down\, Limp Bizkit\, Papa Roach and many more. Metalcore & DnB boosted of course\, HIGH VOLTAGE Style! Vienna’s only Metal & DnB Party ⚡🔥💀 One pit to rule them all: Alternative & Nu Metal\, Metalcore + Drum and Bass 🎧🔥 DJ Rosi: Weberknecht\, WUK\, Ponyhof\, Wirtshausraves & Rinderversteigerungshalle 🎧🔥 DJ wnr: Weberknecht\, Wirtshausraves\, Rhiz & Underground Raves 🔊 Sounds Like: Linkin Park | Korn | Slipknot | System of a Down | Skindred | Limp Bizkit | Papa Roach | Breaking Benjamin | Three Days Grace | Godsmack | P.O.D | Static-X | Shinedown | Hollywood Undead | Disturbed | Deftones | Electric Callboy | Bring Me the Horizon | Motionless in White | Architects | I Prevail | Polaris | Nothing More | Escape the Fate | Bad Omens | BABYMETAL | Poppy | In This Moment | Beartooth | Falling in Reverse | Avenged Sevenfold | Rise Against | Parkway Drive | A Day to Remember | Ice Nine Kills | Enter Shikari | Landmvrks | Bullet for My Valentine | My Chemical Romance | Black Veil Brides | The Offspring | Sum 41 | Paramore | Evanescence | Pierce the Veil | Asking Alexandria | Thousand Foot Krutch | Pendulum | Chase & Status | The Prodigy | The Qemists | Solence | Zardonic | Kanine | Camo & Krooked | Dimension | Sub Focus | Culture Shock | Mefjus | Noisia | Insideinfo | Pythius | Freaks & Geeks | Kritikal | Riot 🤌 Goodies: 😎 Summer Goodies to cool off ❄️ 🧚‍♀️💙 Fairy Juice = Gratis Eintritts-Shots 🥃 👑 Knicklichtern & LED-Kronen 💖💫 Merch Stand: Schnapp dir High Voltage Fairies (HVF) Merch günstiger als online\, mit HVF-Merch bekommst du halben Eintritt bei unseren Events! Limited Online Presale: Early Bird Tickets: 7€ Abendkassa: Im Feen-Kostüm / HVF-Merch: 6€ | Standard: 10€    
